{"tid":770423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"於方國珊辦事處門外大叫「我要搵哪吒」 文員遊蕩今判感化令","createTime":"2018-08-07T05:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T06:34:39.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d73e59e0c4dd5f60316081fb7ca969874587dc0a","tid":770423,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180807/large/1533620080_25aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180807%2Flarge%2F1533620080_25aa.jpg&h=95027536&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 方國珊<br />\n<br />\n63歲文員去年5月31日下午走到西貢區議員方國珊的議員辦事處不斷敲門，又大叫「我要搵哪吒」，並一時跪地一時走來走去，事件擾攘近30分鐘，方認為受到滋擾於是報警。文員早前承認遊蕩導致他人擔心罪，今被判接受感化令12個月。<br />\n<br />\n辯方今指，被告田偉靈願意遵從特定條件，亦會珍惜法庭給予的機會，而被告的感化報告亦建議被告接受感化。裁判官遂接納建議，但提醒被告須在指定地方居住、遵從感化官的指派，若有需要須參與心理及精神治療、參與小組訓練等。<br />\n<br />\n被告田偉靈被控於2017年5月31日，在將軍澳善明邨善智樓地下方國珊議員辦事處外遊蕩，令方國珊擔心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180807/58533149\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180807%2F58533149&d=gV%2FhBUUaK4F2E3PEbKxKdqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=64425a96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180807%2F58533149&h=d7f8a27a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180807/58533149</a>"},{"pid":"00d10a3058764651a46e98323ced9452bd361f22","tid":770423,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:42:46.000Z","msg":"涉於方國珊辦事處外徘徊 男子今否認遊蕩罪<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/593498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/593498</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dbe9c62af20680b29e272a23a66b73a72910e501","tid":770423,"uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://puui.qpic.cn/qqvideo_ori/0/l05639p4z8d_496_280/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuui.qpic.cn%2Fqqvideo_ori%2F0%2Fl05639p4z8d_496_280%2F0&h=7e19ee33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"483694f4d9310b659d29e2f1d011abb788f8ebd8","tid":770423,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c222fe79e43719ea75d5d4515a50e9318b66b5","tid":770423,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T05:48:15.000Z","msg":"傻人發現案"},{"pid":"9935cfb14ff5e24cf2728969c8c2c1f65c99e7f2","tid":770423,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:21:22.000Z","msg":"暴君!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"0338763954f397c5e2d1df5bf864c039f7ab131b","tid":770423,"uid":37528,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"反而唱歌妖孽咁令人不安又騷擾就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b656374452b149d90443236cbef0f0fdae2d2009","tid":770423,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:24:17.000Z","msg":"但係佢自己競選嗰時個名都（哪吒）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe1c45db13d9ec8d46846266dca33e0ebf70eab","tid":770423,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160330/photo/bkn-20160330005131011-0330_00862_001_01p.jpg?20160401121837\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2